  "detailed_description": "Currently, At the early access version, we have a few game modes for players.<br><strong>1. 1v1 duel</strong><br><strong>2. 8 players brawl</strong><br><strong>3. Dungeon Design</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Duel game mode</h2>Have a fair competition with other players<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897890/extras/aad2d1c5e2de97e328c8f5fec6399ba5.poster.avif?t=1610134897\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897890/extras/aad2d1c5e2de97e328c8f5fec6399ba5.webm?t=1610134897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897890/extras/aad2d1c5e2de97e328c8f5fec6399ba5.mp4?t=1610134897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Brawl game mode</h2>The equipment will be randomly assigned to the treasure chest on an island.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897890/extras/2d3be0bb2ecd8f12fa4933ed9dce2563.poster.avif?t=1610134897\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897890/extras/2d3be0bb2ecd8f12fa4933ed9dce2563.webm?t=1610134897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897890/extras/2d3be0bb2ecd8f12fa4933ed9dce2563.mp4?t=1610134897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>At Dungeon maker, you can design your own dungeon and place monsters,<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897890/extras/70686953220517a06a99c380bb3c10b6.poster.avif?t=1610134897\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897890/extras/70686953220517a06a99c380bb3c10b6.webm?t=1610134897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897890/extras/70686953220517a06a99c380bb3c10b6.mp4?t=1610134897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Also, you can download another player dungeon for you to explore.<br>Challenge the ranking of dungeons and get some rewards.<br><br>Discord! : <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897890/extras/f932477da6ead5f5fd7c09b80d573300.avif?t=1610134897\" width=600 height=1200 /></span>",
